      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. Can you show me the math for a $400,000 loan? Like, if I'm in year 5 vs year 25, how much of the monthly payment is actually hitting the principal vs the interest? I want to see the actual difference so I can wrap my head around it.",
